nd timely reflection on the important challenge of insuring the continued liveability and aesthetic valorization of public spaces.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aArchitecture and society. 0aArt and society. 0aCities and towns. 0aCity planning. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh1 aFederici, Corrado, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978077355235740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773552357423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773552357/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles